                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17650710-47-off252 t17650710-47-crimeloc255"></join>. On the 31st of May, about four in the afternoon, the prisoner stood loitering about my door for some time; 
               <persName id="t17650710-47-person483">
                  Henry 
                  Cook 
               <interp inst="t17650710-47-person483" type="surname" value="Cook"></interp>
