             came and told me he saw the prisoner take a pair of shoes from off the corner of the window; I ran out, and in an hundred yards catched him by the shoulders; I saw he had the shoes, and made him bring them back again, and deliver them at the door: I took him before the Justice; he committed him to New Prison.</p>
               <p>Q. Where was you at the time he took them?</p>
               <p>Taylor. I was at work in the shop, on the other side the window?</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17650710-47-person484">
                  Henry 
                  Cook 
               <interp inst="t17650710-47-person484" type="surname" value="Cook"></interp>
