                  </persName>
            . I live next door to Mr. Taylor; I saw the prisoner loitering by the shop, and at last take a pair of shoes from the window, and was going off with them: I went and informed Mr. Taylor of it; he went and brought him back with the shoes.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I was a little in liquor; this is the first thing of that fort that ever I did.</p>
